Hey, it's you. Are you
joining the self-defense
corps? ...Haha, just kidding.

rows.label: tlk41300022_07_msg0001

Ah, I was just giving instructions
to my comrades in the corps.

rows.label: tlk41300022_07_msg0002
rows.name:
The number of Superbian immigrants has
increased, you see. It'll be too late
if we wait for a problem to occur.

rows.label: tlk41300022_07_msg0003

Before I knew it, I became a veteran
in the self-defense corps. I have
to be firm at times like these!
